{
  "_meta": {
    "description": "NASCAR Points Analysis palette — team-keyed layout (2026-04 refactor).",
    "layout": [
      "`teams` — one entry per team code (JGR, RCR, KR, ...). `org` is the team",
      "  brand color used for team pills & teammate group cards. `full_name` and",
      "  `pill_label` replace the JS-side TEAM_FULL_NAMES / TEAM_PILL_LABELS maps.",
      "  Team codes are emitted by scrape_points.py via team_codes.py; one team code",
      "  == one team across every series and every season.",
      "`W`/`B`/`C` — per-car accent colors keyed by car number. ONLY `car` lives here.",
      "  The render layer derives `org` at display time from the driver's team_code",
      "  via the `teams` map above. Adding a new driver no longer requires editing",
      "  this file unless you want a custom accent color — team identity just works."
    ],
    "source": "TRD-provided for NOS; derived from team brand colors for NCS and NTS",
    "special": { "leader_lap_down": "#FEFEFE" }
  },

